**Options considered:**
1. Fix only Notes.tsx (immediate bug)
2. Fix all high-risk components (Notes, ImageNode, Calendars)
3. Fix entire platform (all 24 files)

**Chosen:** Option 2 (high-risk components)

**Rationale:**
- Addresses confirmed bug + high-risk issues (80/20 rule)
- Manageable scope (~90 min)
- Creates reusable pattern for future use
- Low-risk components already use safe patterns

